<div id="outline-container-sec-25" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-25"><span class="section-number-2">25</span> Receiving the packet</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-25">
<p>
[[#][<i>images/arrow.png</i>]]
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-25-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-25-1">Receiving the packet</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-25-1">
<p>
Nearly there now.
</p>

<p>
To finish off scripting the following needs to happen.
</p>

<p>
The laptop has to listen out for the packet to broadcast <code>arrived</code>
</p>

<p>
When this happends it can say the contents of the <code>packet_list</code>
</p>

<p>
[[#][<i>images/arrow.png</i>]]
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-25-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-25-2">Pseudocode</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-25-2">
<pre class="example">
when I receive arrived
if touching packet
    say (join "Received " (join item 2 of packet_list (join " from " item 1 of packet_list)))
</pre>

<p>
[[#][<i>images/arrow.png</i>]]
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-25-3" class="outline-3">
