<div id="outline-container-sec-26-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-26-1">Studying the network</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-26-1">
<p>
Play around with your network by clicking on different laptops and
entering data and an IP address to send it to.
</p>

<p>
Make sure you understand the basics of how the network works
</p>

<p>
Remember - <i>this is an oversimplification but it should give you an
idea.</i>
</p>

<p>
You can find a working model
<a href="http://scratch.mit.edu/projects/11937692/">here</a> if your's doesn't
work.
</p>

<p>
[[#][<i>images/arrow.png</i>]]
</p>
</div>
