<div id="outline-container-sec-27-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-27-1">Below are a series of extension activites.</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-27-1">
<p>
Choose an activity or activities that you feel will stretch your
abilities but that you feel comfortable with.
</p>

<p>
[[#][<i>images/arrow.png</i>]]
</p>
</div>
