<div id="outline-container-sec-27-4" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-27-4">How the Internet works.</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-27-4">
<p>
Using any software you desire:
</p>

<p>
Create a presentation, poster or report to explaian how the internet
works. Include:
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>What a packet is
</li>
<li>What a router is
</li>
<li>How a packet is transmitted from one computer to another
</li>
</ul>

<p>
Make sure the product you create is suitable for a person who know
little about the Internet/
</p>

<p>
Make sure to include some information that you have gathered
independently.
</p>
</div>
